are none of my business.

587
00:35:38,080 --> 00:35:38,840
Is that clear?

588
00:35:40,200 --> 00:35:41,000
Are you sure?

589
00:35:42,200 --> 00:35:42,960
Give me a break.

590
00:35:43,040 --> 00:35:44,000
No one gets it.

591
00:35:44,080 --> 00:35:45,000
Leave me alone!

592
