Come out.

595
00:36:13,560 --> 00:36:14,120
Your Majesty.

596
00:36:22,200 --> 00:36:23,040
Why are you here?

597
00:36:23,760 --> 00:36:24,840
The Chess Overseer

598
00:36:24,840 --> 00:36:25,840
