698
00:41:28,920 --> 00:41:29,560
So

699
00:41:30,800 --> 00:41:31,640
what about now?

700
00:41:32,480 --> 00:41:34,360
I must remind myself at all times

701
00:41:37,240 --> 00:41:38,800
